name: Alyssa Milano LoRA
description:
A Stable Diffusion LoRA profile based on Alyssa Milano.

Very annoying how following the same method for each Lora can give amazing results most of the time and then really hit and miss results with another, this is one of the latter, can give amazing renders but may take a few attempts.

Place it in "stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora" folder in Automatic1111 WebUI root folder.

Made using kohya-ss so make sure to have that extension installed!

In txt2img, under "Additional Networks", select "Enable" and under Model 1 select "Alyssa Milano" and assign a weight between 0.3-0.7 (feel free to experiment!). In the prompt text window use "Alyssa Milano" within your prompt to generate images.

Embed has been trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5 model.

I Recommend the model

https://civitai.com/models/4922/grapelikedreamfruit - Gives amazing realistic renders.
